Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.65,0:00:46.32,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}BON-BON Cheerleaders!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.32,0:00:47.89,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let's get! Cherry pie!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.89,0:00:49.48,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}RAN-RAN Welcome party
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.48,0:00:51.09,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Look up! Sensation
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.09,0:00:51.76,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.76,0:00:54.16,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The presence... of asteroids!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.16,0:00:55.76,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}As they confoundedly collide and melt...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.76,0:00:57.54,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sing loudly! Like a Sirenger
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.54,0:00:58.70,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.70,0:01:03.15,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll be the one with the last laugh
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.15,0:01:10.05,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Because I'm wearing a sailor uniform {\fnaquafont\fs34.5}←{\rs}And that's that
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.28,0:01:12.31,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Even though it's only Monday!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.31,0:01:15.80,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm feeling horrible. What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.80,0:01:22.85,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The summer clothes are so much better! {\fnaquafont\fs34.5}←{\rs}Oh, so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.85,0:01:25.96,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's getting close to 3 picts. Yet, I'm still hesitating.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.96,0:01:30.00,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Try your best! Get your spirits up! My Darlin' darlin' PLEASE!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.44,0:00:02.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Class 3-B?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.64,0:00:04.77,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Kuroi!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.77,0:00:05.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.11,0:01:36.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been messing around there for a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.15,0:01:37.27,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but can you even tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.27,0:01:39.05,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't they all the same?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.72,0:01:41.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it common sense to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.26,0:01:43.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, you could spend all the money\N in the world and never get what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.97,0:01:47.05,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Your common sense has very little practical application.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.05,0:01:50.27,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,At the very least, normal people wouldn't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.50,0:01:54.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't just about figures...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.87,0:01:57.58,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Some people are after the cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.58,0:01:59.80,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you distinguish between cards?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.80,0:02:00.93,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't they all weigh the same?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.93,0:02:04.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There have been many legends and rumors about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.47,0:02:06.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Like where to find good cards...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.14,0:02:08.91,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Or special marks or patterns to look for.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.91,0:02:13.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, I can usually get the special cards I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.50,0:02:14.94,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a pattern to it...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.94,0:02:16.12,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...if the box was just opened.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.29,0:02:18.38,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's pretty insane if you think about it...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.38,0:02:19.96,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...but I really don't feel like praising her!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.22,0:02:21.67,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If people know these things...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.67,0:02:23.88,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...don't the good ones get taken in no time?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.11,0:02:25.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.65,0:02:27.20,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If you live in an area with experts...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.20,0:02:31.18,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...rare cards and secret figures are gone in a flash.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.48,0:02:34.93,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,When I go to a shop and see all these gaps in a box...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.93,0:02:36.81,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'm left in despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.80,0:02:40.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But then I end up falling for that faint glimmer of hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.15,0:02:41.09,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's such a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.09,0:02:42.98,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You definitely have a problematic nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.32,0:02:44.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard some collectors...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.78,0:02:47.22,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...go out and buy a whole bunch at once?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.28,0:02:48.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.84,0:02:49.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Some do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.85,0:02:52.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's faster to complete a set if you buy a bunch at once...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.26,0:02:54.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and it's easier to read distribution patterns that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.56,0:02:54.94,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.19,0:02:58.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, they call it the adult purchasing\N method since it's a strain on your budget.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.92,0:03:00.13,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta work part-time to support it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.53,0:03:01.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Adult purchasing method, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.78,0:03:03.63,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They might call it an adult method...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.63,0:03:05.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but they sure act immature.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.59,0:03:07.30,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It signifies a really possessive nature...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.30,0:03:08.89,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...or selfish behavior.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.68,0:03:12.20,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe the young adult purchasing method would be better.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.20,0:03:16.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I the only one who thinks that\N spending the effort on something else...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.39,0:03:17.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...would be more meaningful?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.98,0:03:19.60,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,These days...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.92,0:03:23.63,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Akihabara gets a lot more media attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.03,0:03:26.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And they're obnoxious about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.47,0:03:27.88,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They can do stories if they want...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.88,0:03:30.93,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I have yet to see anything based on factual evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.93,0:03:33.22,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, they probably exaggerate some stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.22,0:03:34.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but isn't that because of their audience?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.69,0:03:37.43,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But that doesn't explain how TV shows and songs...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.43,0:03:40.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...which were big in otaku culture first became popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.49,0:03:44.82,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,News programs and variety shows\N use anime and game music all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.82,0:03:45.57,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.57,0:03:49.38,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe that's because normal people wouldn't recognize it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.66,0:03:51.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of otakus...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.08,0:03:52.55,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Male otakus...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.55,0:03:56.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...are always talking about how they want an\N otaku with the same interests for a girlfriend...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.02,0:03:57.75,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...on forums and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.02,0:04:02.36,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But you never hear a female otaku\N wanting to go out with another otaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.34,0:04:03.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.65,0:04:06.69,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe girls are more susceptible to the charms of 2-D.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.69,0:04:09.76,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe they're worried about the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.76,0:04:12.43,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure most of them are working though...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.43,0:04:13.73,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And like, don't ask me this stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.77,0:04:23.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They showed up as soon as it got hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.56,0:04:25.96,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't stand how they're noisy and quick to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.96,0:04:26.63,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And they're dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.90,0:04:28.69,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They say that Musashi Miyamoto...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.69,0:04:30.86,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...could catch flies using chopsticks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.26,0:04:32.05,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,For real?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.04,0:04:35.72,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe he was willing to\N touch those things with eating utensils.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.72,0:04:36.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Makes me sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.66,0:04:37.58,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's your concern?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.58,0:04:38.60,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I know what you mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.13,0:04:45.82,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Abeshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.70,0:04:48.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.90,0:04:51.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I could never smack a mosquito.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.66,0:04:52.55,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.55,0:04:55.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be all gross when blood got\N over your hand when you crushed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.41,0:04:57.35,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.35,0:04:58.62,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.61,0:05:02.25,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But what if a mosquito lands on your arm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.23,0:05:05.44,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I go, "Shoo! Shoo!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.44,0:05:06.61,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Or I blow on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.28,0:05:10.38,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.38,0:05:12.68,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If you clench your arm when a mosquito lands on it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.68,0:05:14.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...it can't pull its stinger out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.14,0:05:14.82,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.82,0:05:15.62,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Just watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.31,0:05:22.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You are already dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.02,0:05:23.76,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You've already been bitten.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.76,0:05:25.42,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If you clench even harder...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.42,0:05:26.88,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...the mosquito will explode.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.88,0:05:28.25,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.13,0:05:29.96,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(402,609)}It itches!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.51,0:05:32.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Should have just smacked it in the first place.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.96,0:05:32.14,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(402,609)}Itches so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.49,0:05:36.03,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going overseas again this summer, Miyuki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.03,0:05:36.60,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.60,0:05:38.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Not this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.39,0:05:38.99,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.99,0:05:41.25,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...we will probably visit relatives in the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.25,0:05:46.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I also often go to the summer festival\N with the neighbor's daughter from Ryouou.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.50,0:05:48.61,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She's like a younger sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.55,0:05:53.20,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're going to a summer festival, Iwasaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.20,0:05:55.36,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd probably look great in a yukata.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.36,0:05:56.00,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.97,0:05:59.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know that you're complimenting me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.66,0:06:01.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...but for some reason, I can't appreciate it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.87,0:06:03.75,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's like you're saying I don't have any...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.17,0:06:08.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Be right there...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.21,0:06:10.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.50,0:06:11.46,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.46,0:06:12.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You just woke up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.59,0:06:13.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What a slob.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.64,0:06:14.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.45,0:06:17.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Something's really been bothering me lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.34,0:06:17.72,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.18,0:06:20.01,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Like, did my alarm clock ring?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.01,0:06:22.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Or like, did somebody else turn it off?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.85,0:06:25.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I know what you mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.52,0:06:27.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,When you look, the switch is off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.05,0:06:30.17,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But then again, it gets hot in the afternoon...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.17,0:06:32.01,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so I can't really keep sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.01,0:06:33.55,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We're well into the afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.84,0:06:34.95,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Kona-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.95,0:06:36.03,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.03,0:06:36.95,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.85,0:06:38.82,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Izumi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.82,0:06:40.05,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's eat lunch together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.02,0:06:44.43,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I might go home with you, Konata-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.43,0:06:45.33,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Konata.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.13,0:06:48.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are the main characters in those games...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.52,0:06:50.42,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so unconditionally popular?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.42,0:06:51.27,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Beats me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.27,0:06:53.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe 'cause it wouldn't be a game otherwise?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.97,0:06:54.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.97,0:06:57.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to do your homework!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.10,0:07:01.20,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's not like I'm worried or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.12,0:07:03.20,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.20,0:07:04.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it if you say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.46,0:07:06.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Konata.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.03,0:07:09.69,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are the heroines in those games...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.69,0:07:12.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...always cute with great personalities yet unattached?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.90,0:07:14.09,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You can just pick and choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.09,0:07:14.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Beats me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.90,0:07:16.88,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe 'cause it wouldn't be a game otherwise?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.32,0:07:18.93,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, Konata!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.93,0:07:20.28,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here to play!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.28,0:07:22.62,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,While checking on Yutaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.87,0:07:24.27,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening, Cousin Yui.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.52,0:07:25.60,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Konata?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.60,0:07:27.31,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Your father's calling for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.31,0:07:28.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.69,0:07:31.72,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yutaka started on her homework, so let me borrow some manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.72,0:07:32.42,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Er...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.42,0:07:34.57,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you need to study, Konata?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.57,0:07:36.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't you been playing this whole time?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.15,0:07:36.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.84,0:07:37.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got it wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.97,0:07:40.51,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You just have bad timing and enter whenever I'm taking a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.39,0:07:44.77,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord1\c&H7344E8&\3c&H554F83&\pos(100,476)\frz24.688}GRIN
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.39,0:07:44.77,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord1\c&H7344E8&\3c&H554F83&\frz337.981\pos(526,528)}GRIN
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.83,0:07:44.77,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But that just means you take a lot of breaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.77,0:07:45.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.85,0:07:47.79,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'm concerned about my image at home...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.79,0:07:50.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I try to stay at my desk...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.02,0:07:51.42,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I end up taking a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.40,0:07:52.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.71,0:07:55.46,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because you usually don't work hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.93,0:07:56.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.97,0:07:59.20,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I don't understand how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.20,0:08:01.58,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You've had a similar experience?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.58,0:08:02.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.78,0:08:05.62,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If I pick up a book I really want to read during a break...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.62,0:08:08.62,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...I end up wanting to take another\N break as soon as I start studying again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.62,0:08:11.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to put those down in the middle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.71,0:08:12.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same with manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.71,0:08:15.00,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You say you'll stop after one more volume...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.00,0:08:18.55,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but then you end up reading dozens more.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.55,0:08:21.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,When you borrow the DVDs for a TV series you missed...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.26,0:08:22.93,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...you always have to watch one more episode.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.93,0:08:25.83,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But the follow-up tends to be trash.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.81,0:08:27.14,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.14,0:08:30.06,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Director, about this doll...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.27,0:08:28.23,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.23,0:08:30.08,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I change the channel?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.08,0:08:30.89,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.89,0:08:32.98,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't really watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.98,0:08:35.09,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there something you want to watch?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.90,0:08:39.17,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There's going to be a special on sweets from around the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.84,0:08:42.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You love sweets, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.14,0:08:43.41,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet Kagami and Tsukasa will watch, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.79,0:08:50.12,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}It's like the Hare Hare Dance of sweets!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.62,0:08:48.95,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That looks great!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.95,0:08:50.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,With these shows...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.52,0:08:51.98,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...even if you find something good...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.98,0:08:55.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...it ends up being sold somewhere far\N away and you're left disappointed, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.02,0:08:58.03,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We live in Saitama, so Nagoya's kinda...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.03,0:08:59.67,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That always happens...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.67,0:09:01.24,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I still end up watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.24,0:09:02.03,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.60,0:09:06.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Yuki-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.39,0:09:07.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.85,0:09:10.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I went to the dentist's yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.64,0:09:12.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still going?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.39,0:09:14.61,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I ran away halfway through...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.09,0:09:18.51,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me know if it hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.64,0:09:23.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be over soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.70,0:09:26.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Something like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.71,0:09:27.95,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.95,0:09:29.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They never stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.50,0:09:30.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts to just hear about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.92,0:09:33.08,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We already have summer classes...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.08,0:09:34.29,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but homework on top of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.29,0:09:35.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Screw that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.92,0:09:38.00,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's summer vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.00,0:09:40.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like you do it yourself anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.16,0:09:42.01,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.01,0:09:44.22,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...unlike grade school and middle school...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.22,0:09:46.99,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...we don't have independent projects or book reports.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.99,0:09:48.72,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this easier?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.72,0:09:50.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You just have to answer questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.47,0:09:53.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We made crafts and posters, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.56,0:09:54.75,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,With that stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.75,0:09:57.79,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...you end up getting your parents' help.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.79,0:10:01.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And then they get so into it that they finish it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.32,0:10:04.53,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I won a prize off of that once.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.53,0:10:05.80,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,With a poster or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.33,0:10:07.57,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.58,0:10:09.24,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I was like, "It's all thanks to you, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.24,0:10:10.99,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you're even cooler now!"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.99,0:10:13.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And Dad was all happy about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.16,0:10:14.96,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shouldn't a parent be mad about that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.52,0:10:29.81,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Buy at least five at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.08,0:10:31.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever I see this commercial...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.52,0:10:33.98,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...I always get jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.98,0:10:35.25,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was little...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.25,0:10:38.06,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and read that fairy tale about a gingerbread house...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.06,0:10:41.55,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...I wanted to try eating all the candy I could!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.78,0:10:43.13,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I know what you mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.13,0:10:45.88,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but when you actually get a lot of what you want...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.88,0:10:47.79,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...you tend to lose interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.04,0:10:49.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.16,0:10:50.37,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.37,0:10:51.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It stinks the whole year.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.96,0:10:54.12,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So I was thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.12,0:10:55.94,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,About summer homework...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.94,0:10:59.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm always in trouble 'cause I plan\N to do it in one go in the latter half.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.48,0:11:00.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That came out of nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.71,0:11:02.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And I didn't need you to tell me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.76,0:11:05.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If I worked at it little by little...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.26,0:11:07.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...I might not have to scramble at the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.59,0:11:09.60,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You just realized that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.60,0:11:11.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a third-year already.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.26,0:11:13.33,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't burn yourself out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.33,0:11:15.58,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means I'll be coming over tomorrow so thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.58,0:11:17.04,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bring a present.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.38,0:11:19.58,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what you meant by little by little?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.58,0:11:21.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to come over all summer?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.92,0:11:23.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably every week.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.65,0:11:24.37,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.53,0:11:27.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.70,0:11:28.68,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.68,0:11:29.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.45,0:11:30.68,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.68,0:11:32.31,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The A/C's on in my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.27,0:11:34.25,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So comfortable!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.56,0:11:36.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are making yourself at home...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.56,0:11:38.10,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like this every year.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.10,0:11:41.77,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Summer always passes without me wanting to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.77,0:11:44.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Before I know it, summer vacation's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.32,0:11:46.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop sounding so lazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.26,0:11:48.03,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Set milestones this year...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.03,0:11:49.73,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and get your homework done.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.18,0:11:51.30,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.30,0:11:55.25,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I plan on working hard before summer vacation begins every year.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.25,0:11:56.23,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.23,0:11:57.46,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,In manga...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.46,0:12:00.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You see the whole "I didn't do my homework!" gag used a lot...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.15,0:12:01.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...this time of year.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.15,0:12:01.86,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.86,0:12:03.46,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,When you look at that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.46,0:12:07.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...don't you think that in theory, you don't need to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.34,0:12:09.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's what everybody else is doing...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.07,0:12:10.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.45,0:12:10.95,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.95,0:12:12.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, if you're gonna be like this, don't come to copy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.98,0:12:15.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thirsty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.14,0:12:18.06,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go get some barley tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.38,0:12:19.25,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.63,0:12:20.44,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.44,0:12:23.94,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you also get the math problem set from my room?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.94,0:12:24.55,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty please.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.55,0:12:25.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.36,0:12:26.80,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.80,0:12:29.17,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't want to leave an air conditioned room...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.17,0:12:32.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so you ask someone else to do it when they leave...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.45,0:12:35.60,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but nobody else wants to leave, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.00,0:12:38.12,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,In winter, you don't want to leave the kotatsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.12,0:12:40.60,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so you ask someone else to do stuff for you when they get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.60,0:12:41.04,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.29,0:12:42.23,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.23,0:12:43.31,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure is hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.23,0:12:43.31,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1080,679.5)}Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.31,0:12:44.27,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.27,0:12:45.44,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought ice cream.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.44,0:12:48.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Take whichever one you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.92,0:12:51.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I won't be much help with homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.08,0:12:57.41,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And the Marimokkori's eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.52,0:13:00.23,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In these situations...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.23,0:13:04.05,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...why is it that you always want the ones other people chose?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.32,0:13:07.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm reading this manga about getting into Tokyo U.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.09,0:13:09.05,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That one, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.05,0:13:10.24,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,When you read that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.24,0:13:13.20,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...don't you start thinking that you\N might have a chance to get into Tokyo U?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.20,0:13:14.93,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If you work hard like them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.93,0:13:16.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.12,0:13:20.29,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if that method could get you into Tokyo U...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.29,0:13:23.98,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd need friends who abandon their regular classes to join in...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.98,0:13:26.23,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Teachers who hold class like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.23,0:13:27.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone to take charge.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.92,0:13:30.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And all kinds of other things for it to work, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.14,0:13:32.11,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.11,0:13:34.20,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that easy...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.20,0:13:35.49,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Too many people...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.49,0:13:39.60,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...get influenced by manga or TV shows\N and think they can change themselves.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.85,0:13:40.54,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.54,0:13:43.04,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I plan on working hard and studying...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.04,0:13:44.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I always get sleepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.94,0:13:48.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a good way to stay awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.50,0:13:50.21,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's better to take a little nap...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.21,0:13:53.01,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...than to force yourself to stay awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.01,0:13:54.30,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.30,0:13:56.73,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that before, so I gave it a try...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.14,0:13:59.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But my little nap ended up being a lot longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.26,0:13:59.89,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.89,0:14:01.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No willpower...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.62,0:14:02.89,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.89,0:14:04.53,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}Hello, Yutaka-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.31,0:14:04.53,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.53,0:14:06.79,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, do you have a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.79,0:14:08.23,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up, Yu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.23,0:14:10.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You can ask us anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.57,0:14:14.49,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A friend from middle school apparently got a boyfriend...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.49,0:14:18.91,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and she asked me what she should give him for his birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.91,0:14:20.75,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.13,0:14:24.25,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What do I do...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.25,0:14:25.79,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It got really awkward...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.42,0:14:28.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Anyway, Yu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.52,0:14:31.23,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They have web sites that discuss this stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.23,0:14:33.13,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so you should take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.13,0:14:35.38,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There might be a thread about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.38,0:14:37.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You can use my computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.14,0:14:38.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'll do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.48,0:14:40.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I know about Tra** Man...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.64,0:14:43.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but you can even ask questions about this stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.14,0:14:45.73,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty common these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.36,0:14:48.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything goes, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.02,0:14:49.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.34,0:14:52.51,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They probably have the answers for math problems, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.51,0:14:55.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It makes me think how kids these days have it so easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.83,0:14:58.18,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As technology and the community advance...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.18,0:15:01.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...the users' mindsets and willpower are getting worse.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.64,0:15:02.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just look at her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.82,0:15:08.44,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.44,0:15:09.81,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's odd...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.81,0:15:12.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm just copying homework...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.07,0:15:13.28,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...but unlike usual...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.28,0:15:16.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...the presence of an audience creates this pride-like feeling...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.37,0:15:17.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.16,0:15:19.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What about the festival at your place?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.06,0:15:20.51,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.51,0:15:21.51,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's already over.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.51,0:15:21.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.78,0:15:23.29,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Same as last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.29,0:15:25.73,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you tell me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.73,0:15:27.62,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to study for exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.62,0:15:30.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If we told you, you'd definitely want to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.48,0:15:32.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't go either.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.65,0:15:34.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't have to be ours...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.15,0:15:36.57,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Just go to the one where you live.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.57,0:15:37.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it already over?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.58,0:15:39.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Where I live...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.14,0:15:40.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I wonder when that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.85,0:15:42.01,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.01,0:15:44.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Some people go to festivals in other places...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.52,0:15:46.83,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but don't even care about the ones where they live.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.83,0:15:49.63,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you the type who avoids friends from back home?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.23,0:15:54.36,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Even college applicants can't go on studying forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.36,0:15:55.86,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.86,0:15:58.43,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There's going to be a fireworks display near my home tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.76,0:15:59.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.84,0:16:02.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's all go have fun for once!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.00,0:16:04.01,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.01,0:16:05.36,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We could use a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.75,0:16:07.33,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.33,0:16:10.63,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There's going to be a fireworks display\N near your home tomorrow, Minami-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.88,0:16:14.27,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to see Japanese fireworks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.27,0:16:16.63,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's all go together, Minami.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.78,0:16:17.69,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Minami-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.69,0:16:18.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you free tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.90,0:16:19.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.78,0:16:21.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's decided, Minami.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.74,0:16:23.91,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Iwasaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.58,0:16:25.22,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.22,0:16:25.96,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Iwasaki-san?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.39,0:16:29.25,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a pretty famous fireworks display...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.25,0:16:29.94,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...Mi—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.94,0:16:30.77,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Iwasaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.86,0:16:35.40,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's hard to change how you call\N someone once you've gotten used to it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.15,0:16:39.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's far away and famous, so it'll be crowded, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.74,0:16:41.43,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you be okay, Yu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.43,0:16:43.68,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you sick a while back?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.25,0:16:47.79,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's going to be hot tomorrow so should we wait for the next one?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.60,0:16:51.23,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.23,0:16:52.44,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It happens all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.88,0:16:55.75,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the class health officer, and I'll be coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.75,0:16:57.03,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so it'll be okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.59,0:16:58.24,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...Yutaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.14,0:17:00.18,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.35,0:17:01.68,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.68,0:17:03.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Minami-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.83,0:17:07.18,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So we're going to see fireworks...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.18,0:17:09.23,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but otherwise, it's college application and study time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.23,0:17:12.08,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It sucks how I have less time to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.08,0:17:13.88,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause Kagami and the others are all serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.88,0:17:15.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I can understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.65,0:17:18.19,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You should just do what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.18,0:17:21.28,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I used to drag Kanata around...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.28,0:17:23.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and made lots of memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.32,0:17:24.57,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I got in trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.57,0:17:26.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but adolescence doesn't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.78,0:17:30.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then maybe I should get a boyfriend and make some memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.29,0:17:33.10,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Absolutely not!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.10,0:17:34.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't accept a boyfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.48,0:17:35.23,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.23,0:17:36.99,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not making sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.24,0:17:37.86,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.86,0:17:40.24,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna come watch fireworks with us, Yu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.24,0:17:42.30,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I'm also going.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.30,0:17:44.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We're meeting up at Minami-chan's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.89,0:17:45.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.85,0:17:48.60,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We're leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.27,0:17:50.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Have fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.94,0:17:53.51,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The train's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.09,0:17:59.55,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.80,0:18:00.96,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.96,0:18:03.18,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yutaka-chan came along.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.60,0:18:04.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.47,0:18:05.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.39,0:18:06.89,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hey! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.68,0:18:06.89,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.31,0:18:08.35,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.35,0:18:08.89,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.89,0:18:09.60,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.10,0:18:11.31,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Patricia-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.31,0:18:13.46,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you also here for the fireworks?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.46,0:18:14.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You look good in a yukata.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.78,0:18:25.18,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.19,0:18:34.73,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.52,0:18:39.76,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So Miyuki-san's neighbor was Minami-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.05,0:18:41.80,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.80,0:18:43.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.22,0:18:45.11,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.10,0:18:46.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.78,0:18:47.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.83,0:18:49.44,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.70,0:18:50.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Not enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.44,0:18:53.31,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There should be enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.31,0:18:54.27,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.27,0:18:56.61,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you count yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.61,0:18:57.35,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,1.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.35,0:18:57.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,2.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.90,0:18:58.44,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,3.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.44,0:18:59.11,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,4.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.11,0:18:59.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,5.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.65,0:19:00.11,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,6.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.11,0:19:00.61,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,7.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.61,0:19:01.19,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,8.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.19,0:19:01.62,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,9.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.03,0:19:03.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,My.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.07,0:19:03.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.80,0:19:05.91,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now I get it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.18,0:19:08.12,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for having us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.99,0:19:10.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is Minami-chan's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.48,0:19:13.25,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Scary big dog...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.25,0:19:14.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.77,0:19:16.10,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't bark.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.09,0:19:17.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's really friendly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.92,0:19:18.83,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.83,0:19:20.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,When they're big and friendly...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.65,0:19:22.44,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...it's actually kinda cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.72,0:19:23.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.71,0:19:25.22,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's growling at me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.22,0:19:27.95,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Maybe she's the type who tends to get barked at.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.54,0:19:33.79,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was little...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.79,0:19:38.46,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...I would wonder if fireworks were still round from the side.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.84,0:19:39.54,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.54,0:19:41.29,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So they don't look flat?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.29,0:19:42.05,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey now...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.30,0:19:45.82,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They show firework displays on TV occassionally...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.82,0:19:48.89,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but there's a better atmosphere when you watch the real thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.89,0:19:49.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.06,0:19:50.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.78,0:19:52.62,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.62,0:19:54.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time they launch a big one...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.56,0:19:58.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and announce that this was\N sponsored by some business or other...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.90,0:20:00.42,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...doesn't that ruin the mood?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.80,0:20:02.13,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.44,0:20:03.17,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.17,0:20:03.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.92,0:20:05.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You look a little pale.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.36,0:20:07.35,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.06,0:20:11.68,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.68,0:20:13.06,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so go watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.06,0:20:13.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.96,0:20:14.99,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.58,0:20:16.77,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.77,0:20:17.83,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Minami-chan.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.67,0:20:24.36,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That was wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.36,0:20:25.17,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.17,0:20:27.38,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is what summer's all about.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.38,0:20:28.05,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.55,0:20:33.33,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It never ends up being a beautiful memory like in manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.33,0:20:35.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I got bitten everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.14,0:20:35.93,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So itchy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.31,0:20:38.77,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They say that it itches more if you scratch.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.77,0:20:42.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And when you take off the yukata, it itches under the belt.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.90,0:20:43.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.49,0:20:45.46,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.46,0:20:47.49,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It really was.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.49,0:20:50.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But sorry for causing you trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.64,0:20:52.55,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.55,0:20:53.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.87,0:20:56.37,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you guys bitten by bugs, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.62,0:20:59.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We weren't bitten at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.63,0:21:04.42,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So some people are easily bitten and some aren't.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.42,0:21:05.44,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.44,0:21:06.28,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.28,0:21:07.95,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe the mosquitos read the mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.70,0:21:15.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Good lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.56,0:21:18.58,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm your navigator, Akira Kogami!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.90,0:21:20.37,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the assistant...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.37,0:21:21.76,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Daisuke Ono.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.76,0:21:24.76,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We're already on the twentieth episode of Lucky Channel!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.32,0:21:26.93,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not a crow today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.11,0:21:29.93,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not a dog today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.57,0:21:32.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's have a look at the live feed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.83,0:21:37.37,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder where he is right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.37,0:21:38.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That Shiroishi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.58,0:21:40.96,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mt. Fuji's so pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.52,0:21:42.29,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.77,0:21:44.10,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then bye-bee!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.10,0:21:45.00,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bee!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.55,0:21:47.38,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiraishi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.55,0:21:49.38,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiraishi-kun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.06,0:23:24.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, next time on Lucky Star:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.39,0:23:25.12,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Misao here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.12,0:23:25.83,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayano here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.83,0:23:26.69,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ayano.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.69,0:23:28.44,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't Hiiragi so heartless?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.44,0:23:30.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She always runs off to the midget's class.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.65,0:23:31.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.65,0:23:34.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Does our love not reach Hiiragi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.49,0:23:35.35,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.35,0:23:36.72,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Pandora's Box.
