Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.84,0:21:54.64,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.64,0:21:55.93,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs72}This{\fs45} is what you wanted, right{\fs72}?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.26,0:21:57.62,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}Hello, Minoru Shiraishi here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.62,0:21:59.58,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}Now, please listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.58,0:22:00.75,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}Bridegroom Rumba!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.43,0:22:03.10,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}One, two, three, four!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.64,0:22:20.31,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Merry voices ring through the air...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.31,0:22:23.89,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,...at a church in June.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.89,0:22:27.90,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,The phrase "happiest moment of my life" was...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.90,0:22:31.82,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,...made for such a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.86,0:22:35.41,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'd known this would happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.41,0:22:38.87,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,...I wouldn't have bought that new house.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.87,0:22:42.75,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Getting jilted by the bride...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.75,0:22:46.38,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,...is like something out of manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.38,0:22:50.00,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,All worked up, I break into the Bridegroom Rumba.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.00,0:22:51.84,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody save me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.84,0:22:53.63,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my god!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.63,0:22:57.22,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I going to do now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.24,0:23:00.64,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Even my boss is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.43,0:23:03.35,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, three! Two, Two, three!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.35,0:23:05.94,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Bridegroom Rumba!
